<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4036609" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">不能忍，这么多人居然连个弓箭协会会徽都不给，题主我是来给你送会徽的，快笑纳！<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/b3580fd5d0ffa76cfa52b1fc27cd51c9_b.jpg" data-rawheight="556" data-rawwidth="560" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="560" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/b3580fd5d0ffa76cfa52b1fc27cd51c9_r.jpg"><br>取名嘛，可以取<strong>箭男部落<br></strong><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/0f161663f1a12d310c9029d81c493048_b.jpg" data-rawheight="1277" data-rawwidth="1600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1600" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/0f161663f1a12d310c9029d81c493048_r.jpg"><br><br>或者，<strong>大正弓娘组合</strong><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/6a0ddc4856d341aa39e8ef293a12f602_b.jpg" data-rawheight="1023" data-rawwidth="1600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1600" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/6a0ddc4856d341aa39e8ef293a12f602_r.jpg"><br><br>逼格都很高。。。。。。<br><br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/1842fe9264c382f274536ae4e1bc16ea_b.jpg" data-rawheight="763" data-rawwidth="1100" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1100" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/1842fe9264c382f274536ae4e1bc16ea_r.jpg">我知道我击沉了各位舰队娘控的大正娘梦我勒个擦。<br><br>当然，还有比如<strong>一射一身协会</strong>这种立意比较邪恶的<br><br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/8df045c0d22c7d90da5e47017a3ed585_b.jpg" data-rawheight="348" data-rawwidth="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/8df045c0d22c7d90da5e47017a3ed585_r.jpg"><br>当当然，还有比较温馨一点的<strong>大家一起射吧</strong>。。。。。。当然名字逼格不够高，贴吧味很重。。。。。。<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e70c5a259c02a5908c3202c01467ceda_b.jpg" data-rawheight="500" data-rawwidth="388" class="content_image" width="388"><br>以及，基友铁不铁，<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/8e342bcf4913f051644ad84461a00aa8_b.jpg" data-rawheight="827" data-rawwidth="620" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/8e342bcf4913f051644ad84461a00aa8_r.jpg"><br>相聚在射箭。。。。。。<br><br>童鞋们要说金老湿你够了，金老湿你耍的一手好萌，啊啊啊啊。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。
